Java Architecture
Create .java file (eg. Main.java), save file as class name, here in our context class is Main, so file should be Main.java
Javac – creates .class (bytecode) file (eg. Main.class), now you will have Main.java and Main.class files in your folder.
Java – run/interpret Main class (eg. Java Main or java one.java (if filename is not as class name) using JVM.
Java Buzzwords
1. Simple
•	Java removes complex features like pointers and operator overloading (from C++) 
•	Easy to learn and write 
________________________________________
2. Object-Oriented
•	Everything is based on objects and classes 
•	Supports: 
o	Encapsulation 
o	Inheritance 
o	Polymorphism 
